        "avatar_template": "/user_avatar/community.signalusers.org/devnull42/{size}/33491_2.png",
        "created_at": "2022-10-13T15:47:55.137Z",
        "cooked": "<p>Thanks for linking that thread. It‚Äôs indeed similar and I mentioned my use case over there.</p>\n<p>Just a little side note here: I noticed that the notification profiles feature supports showing notifications only if the message contains <span class=\"mention\">@mentions</span>. So basically the use case I mentioned could be easily covered by just allowing <span class=\"mention\">@mentions</span> in normal (non-group) chats.</p>",
